            <div type="a">
                <column>04</column>
                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p/>
                </transcript>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The National Intelligencer alleges that the Radical Republicans are
                    planning to send secret agents into the South to create disturbances and riots
                    that will turn public opinion to their side and aid them in impeaching President
                    Johnson. The article warns southern whites to remain calm and do nothing that
                    can give the Radicals a political edge.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
